data.description: A fantastic 2bed/1.1bath condo in a prime location- surrounded by everything that Old Town, River North & Lincoln Park have to offer! The home features an open kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertop, large breakfast bar, hardwood flooring through out the living space, in-unit washer/dryer, spacious bedrooms, oversized full bathroom & powder room for guests. Enjoy the convenience of first floor living with a gated entrance, covered back porch and one parking space included.
